PrecisAmendment to the PENSION BENEFITS STANDARDS REGULATIONS, 1985 providing, that where a bank, trust company or other financial institution holds an investment of a pension fund in trust for the fund, the investment is to be registered in the name of the bank, trust company or other financial institution.

precis:
Amendment to the PENSION BENEFITS STANDARDS REGULATIONS, 1985 providing,
that where a bank, trust company or other financial institution holds an
investment of a pension fund in trust for the fund, the investment is to
be registered in the name of the bank, trust company or other financial
institution.
